---
title: Group Module - Swimlane Diagram
description: Cross-functional flow showing interactions between different actors and systems
date: 07-03-26
---

sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User (Owner/Admin)
    participant F as Frontend (Web/Mobile)
    participant API as API Layer
    participant GC as Group Controller
    participant GS as Group Service
    participant GM as Group Member Service
    participant GI as Group Invitation Service
    participant DB as MongoDB
    participant Redis as Redis Cache
    participant Queue as BullMQ
    participant ES as Email Service
    participant N as Notification Service
    
    %% Create Group Flow
    U->>F: Create Group Request
    F->>API: POST /groups
    API->>GC: create()
    GC->>GS: validateGroupData()
    GS->>DB: Check Name Uniqueness
    DB-->>GS: Name Available
    GS->>DB: Insert Group Document
    DB-->>GS: Group Created {_id}
    GS->>GM: Create Owner Membership
    GM->>DB: Insert groupmember (Owner)
    DB-->>GM: Membership Created
    GS->>Redis: Cache Group Data
    GS-->>GC: Group Object
    GC-->>F: 201 Created + Group Data
    F-->>U: Group Created Successfully
    
    %% Invite Members Flow
    U->>F: Invite Members
    F->>API: POST /groups/:id/invitations
    API->>GI: createInvitation()
    GI->>DB: Check Group Exists
    DB-->>GI: Group Found
    GI->>DB: Check Member Limit
    DB-->>GI: Within Limit
    GI->>DB: Create Invitation
    DB-->>GI: Invitation Created
    GI->>Queue: Queue Email Job
    Queue->>ES: Send Invitation Email
    ES-->>GI: Email Sent
    GI->>N: Send In-App Notification
    N-->>GI: Notification Sent
    GI-->>F: 201 Created + Invitation
    F-->>U: Invitations Sent
    
    %% Member Accepts Invitation
    Note over U,ES: Member receives email
    Member->>F: Click Accept Link
    F->>API: POST /invitations/:id/accept
    API->>GI: acceptInvitation()
    GI->>DB: Validate Invitation
    DB-->>GI: Valid & Not Expired
    GI->>GM: Add Member to Group
    GM->>DB: Insert groupmember
    DB-->>GM: Member Added
    GI->>DB: Update Invitation Status
    GI->>Redis: Invalidate Cache
    GI->>N: Notify Owner
    N-->>U: New Member Joined
    GI-->>F: 200 OK + Member Data
    
    %% View Group Members
    U->>F: View Members
    F->>API: GET /groups/:id/members
    API->>GM: getGroupMembers()
    GM->>Redis: Check Cache
    Redis-->>GM: Cache Miss
    GM->>DB: Query Members with Populates
    DB-->>GM: Member List
    GM->>Redis: Cache Results (5min)
    GM-->>API: Member List
    API-->>F: 200 OK + Members
    F-->>U: Display Members
    
    %% Update Member Role
    U->>F: Promote Member to Admin
    F->>API: PUT /groups/:id/members/:userId/role
    API->>GM: updateMemberRole()
    GM->>DB: Check Owner Permission
    DB-->>GM: Is Owner ✅
    GM->>DB: Update Member Role
    DB-->>GM: Role Updated
    GM->>Redis: Invalidate Cache
    GM->>N: Notify Member
    N-->>Member: You're Now Admin
    GM-->>API: 200 OK + Updated Member
    F-->>U: Role Updated Successfully
    
    %% Remove Member
    U->>F: Remove Member
    F->>API: DELETE /groups/:id/members/:userId
    API->>GM: removeMember()
    GM->>DB: Check Permission
    DB-->>GM: Is Owner/Admin ✅
    GM->>DB: Soft Delete Membership
    DB-->>GM: Member Removed
    GM->>DB: Update Group Member Count
    GM->>Redis: Invalidate Cache
    GM->>N: Notify Removed Member
    GM-->>API: 200 OK
    F-->>U: Member Removed
    
    %% Leave Group
    Member->>F: Leave Group
    F->>API: POST /groups/:id/leave
    API->>GM: leaveGroup()
    GM->>DB: Check Is Not Owner
    DB-->>GM: Not Owner ✅
    GM->>DB: Soft Delete Membership
    DB-->>GM: Left Group
    GM->>DB: Decrement Member Count
    GM->>Redis: Invalidate Cache
    GM-->>API: 200 OK
    F-->>Member: Left Group Successfully
    
    %% Delete Group
    U->>F: Delete Group
    F->>API: DELETE /groups/:id
    API->>GC: deleteById()
    GC->>GS: Check Owner Permission
    GS->>DB: Verify Owner
    DB-->>GS: Is Owner ✅
    GS->>DB: Soft Delete Group
    GS->>GM: Archive All Memberships
    GM->>DB: Soft Delete Memberships
    GS->>GI: Cancel Pending Invitations
    GI->>DB: Mark Invitations Expired
    GS->>Redis: Clear Cache
    GS-->>GC: Group Deleted
    GC-->>F: 200 OK
    F-->>U: Group Deleted Successfully
    
    Note over U,N: All actions trigger notifications
